                            "2": {
                              "id": "2",
                              "speaker": "Mortarch Gracie Scyre",
                              "text": "Do you feel that warmth in your heart at his memory? Death does not mean you are apart - he is here every time you speak of him.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: gentle, touching her heart and then bending down to point at Nina's (she's right in front of her). Thr motach has a very comfortable relationship with death and wants nina to have the same",
